00:37:33,630 --> 00:37:34,360
What about the other one?

606
00:37:34,850 --> 00:37:35,630
Massive hemorrhage

607
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:36,510
from internal injuries.

608
00:37:36,670 --> 00:37:37,760
We'll do our best.

609
00:38:04,550 --> 00:38:05,070
Captain Peng.

610
00:38:06,230 --> 00:38:06,830
How is it?

611
00:38:07,300 --> 00:38:08,480
Shoujia's out of danger.

612
00:38:08,510 --> 00:38:09,740
He's in the ward now.

613
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:10,480
And...

614
00:38:11,510 --> 00:38:12,680
Yang Bo is still in rescue.

615
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:13,550
It's okay.

616
00:38:14,150 --> 00:38:15,190
It'll be fine. Don't worry.

617
00:38:40,230 --> 00:38:40,760
How is it?

618
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:41,820
He broke four ribs

619
00:38:42,110 --> 00:38:42,880
and ruptured

620
00:38:42,900 --> 00:38:43,980
the blood vessels in his lungs and chest.

621
00:38:44,110 --> 00:38:44,850
Massive hemorrhage

622
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:46,070
caused various organ failure.

623
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:47,280
The bleeding has stopped.

624
00:38:47,590 --> 00:38:48,710
But whether he can wake up

625
00:38:48,820 --> 00:38:50,260
will depend on his willpower.

626
00:38:50,330 --> 00:38:51,690
We'll keep observing him.

627
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:55,000
Doctor!

628
00:38:55,030 --> 00:38:56,230
Please do your best!

629
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:23,110
Why are you sleeping here?

630
00:39:25,070 --> 00:39:26,230
Answer me! Get up!

631
00:39:27,550 --> 00:39:28,550
Get your director here.

632
00:39:29,350 --> 00:39:30,390
I want to see your director!

633
00:39:34,190 --> 00:39:34,630
Director Xu.

634
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:35,190
Zhaolin.

635
00:39:35,440 --> 00:39:35,880
Come in.

636
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:37,630
Have a seat.

637
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:43,710
How are the injured comrades?

638
00:39:45,730 --> 00:39:47,690
Ge Shoujia just got out of danger.

639
00:39:48,480 --> 00:39:49,070
Yang Bo...

640
00:39:50,620 --> 00:39:51,750
is still in a coma.

641
00:39:55,970 --> 00:39:57,040
We must do our best to save

642
00:39:57,070 --> 00:39:57,800
our comrades.

643
00:39:57,960 --> 00:39:58,400
Yes.

644
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:00,150
Also, what's up

645
00:40:00,150 --> 00:40:01,070
with Huang Qi?

646
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:02,840
I...

647
00:40:04,310 --> 00:40:05,310
I forgot about him.

648
00:40:05,630 --> 00:40:06,800
Alright, sit down.

649
00:40:07,150 --> 00:40:08,030
He's gone.

650
00:40:08,230 --> 00:40:09,070
I sent him off myself.

651
00:40:09,630 --> 00:40:10,210
I even spent

652
00:40:10,240 --> 00:40:11,570
half an hour placating him.

653
00:40:16,710 --> 00:40:17,320
I think

654
00:40:18,230 --> 00:40:19,280
Deng Ligang would've contacted him

655
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:20,960
in this return.

656
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:24,230
Do you have evidence?

657
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:28,070
My two comrades

658
00:40:28,770 --> 00:40:30,440
were almost killed by Deng Ligang.

659
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:32,670
Isn't that evidence?

660
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:34,030
Zhaolin.

661
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:35,630
Right now,

662
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:37,180
you need to stay calm.

663
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:44,920
Director Xu.

664
00:40:48,710 --> 00:40:49,920
Since I accepted this case,

665
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,150
I've always been very calm.

666
00:40:54,110 --> 00:40:55,360
I demand myself to be so.

667
00:40:57,550 --> 00:40:58,800
But one of my comrades

668
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:01,920
just got out of danger

669
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:04,670
and another's life is on the line.

670
00:41:06,070 --> 00:41:06,670
We haven't

671
00:41:07,570 --> 00:41:08,820
made any headway with the case.

672
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:12,250
I don't know

673
00:41:13,060 --> 00:41:13,510
how to

674
00:41:13,510 --> 00:41:14,880
answer to their families.

675
00:41:18,630 --> 00:41:19,190
You can't

676
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,550
be emotional with investigations.

677
00:41:22,030 --> 00:41:22,590
Let me ask you.

678
00:41:22,810 --> 00:41:23,690
How long have you been

679
00:41:23,720 --> 00:41:24,600
in charge of the 11/03 case?

680
00:41:25,110 --> 00:41:25,630
Three months.

681
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:26,480
In three months,

682
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:28,480
two of our men got hurt,

683
00:41:28,660 --> 00:41:29,990
but the case is still stagnant.

684
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:31,320
Also,

685
00:41:31,710 --> 00:41:32,590
on New Year's Eve,

686
00:41:33,480 --> 00:41:34,230
your wife and child

687
00:41:34,230 --> 00:41:35,670
sent you food at your stakeout.

688
00:41:36,750 --> 00:41:37,880
This is prohibited.

689
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:45,230
The Bureau Committee has decided.

690
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:46,520
Someone else will

691
00:41:46,550 --> 00:41:47,440
take over the 11/03 case.

692
00:41:47,630 --> 00:41:48,670
You'll be transferred to Outsourcing.

693
00:41:59,860 --> 00:42:00,300
Director Xu.

694
00:42:00,630 --> 00:42:01,480
Okay, enough.

695
00:42:06,060 --> 00:42:07,060
I'll be frank with you.

696
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:08,320
It's not just you.

697
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:09,960
I received a formal transfer too.

698
00:42:10,060 --> 00:42:11,140
I'm leaving tomorrow.

699
00:42:37,000 --> 00:42:37,800
Aren't you going to work?

700
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:40,710
I'll be

701
00:42:40,880 --> 00:42:41,760
quite free now.

702
00:42:43,070 --> 00:42:43,800
What do you mean?

703
00:42:45,280 --> 00:42:45,840
What's wrong?

704
00:42:48,070 --> 00:42:50,070
I was transferred out of Special Task Force.

705
00:42:52,280 --> 00:42:52,920
Why?

706
00:42:55,550 --> 00:42:56,630
I didn't do my job well.

707
00:42:57,500 --> 00:42:58,660
Still not good enough?

708
00:42:59,410 --> 00:43:00,640
What'll be good enough then?

709
00:43:00,710 --> 00:43:01,610
Never going home?

710
00:43:06,130 --> 00:43:07,740
This case's been open for three months.

711
00:43:09,230 --> 00:43:10,070
I made no progress.

712
00:43:11,370 --> 00:43:12,050
Shoujia

713
00:43:12,160 --> 00:43:13,090
and Yang Bo

714
00:43:13,550 --> 00:43:14,400
are also hospitalized.

715
00:43:15,320 --> 00:43:15,880
What happened?

716
00:43:17,800 --> 00:43:18,230
Exhaustion.

717
00:43:18,880 --> 00:43:19,400
They're fine.

718
00:43:23,450 --> 00:43:24,440
But I'm responsible for this.

719
00:43:25,220 --> 00:43:26,030
I have to...

720
00:43:27,400 --> 00:43:28,190
be punished.

721
00:43:30,150 --> 00:43:31,960
Why should you be punished?

722
00:43:33,040 --> 00:43:34,080
I'm the captain.

723
00:43:41,190 --> 00:43:41,800
Just wait.

724
00:43:42,680 --> 00:43:43,680
This case

725
00:43:44,500 --> 00:43:45,540
needs you.

726
00:43:50,190 --> 00:43:51,300
I need you too.

727
00:43:54,360 --> 00:43:56,070
Spend some time with me and our kid.

728
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:57,770
Rest for a few days.

729
00:43:58,590 --> 00:43:59,670
You're a tough man.

730
00:44:00,030 --> 00:44:00,920
Don't burn out.

731
00:44:09,230 --> 00:44:09,630
Bomb.

732
00:44:09,790 --> 00:44:10,800
Huh? What bomb?

733
00:44:10,820 --> 00:44:11,810
There's no bomb with

734
00:44:11,840 --> 00:44:12,280
three cards.

735
00:44:12,280 --> 00:44:13,000
It's not a bomb?

736
00:44:13,150 --> 00:44:13,880
It's not.

737
00:44:14,360 --> 00:44:14,880
Then what is it?

738
00:44:14,900 --> 00:44:15,300
Oh my.

739
00:44:15,590 --> 00:44:16,380
Playing with Boss Lady...

740
00:44:18,210 --> 00:44:19,110
Where have you been?

741
00:44:37,030 --> 00:44:37,760
The meat's cooked.

742
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:39,320
Come on.

743
00:44:53,230 --> 00:44:54,070
What's this for?

744
00:44:54,960 --> 00:44:55,480
Captain Peng.

745
00:44:56,110 --> 00:44:57,070
How'd we have the appetite?

746
00:44:57,630 --> 00:44:58,280
Yang Bo

747
00:44:58,730 --> 00:44:59,250
and Ge Shoujia

748
00:44:59,280 --> 00:45:00,440
are bedridden in the hospital.

749
00:45:01,350 --> 00:45:02,170
The case's been stopped.

750
00:45:02,760 --> 00:45:03,760
You were transferred.

751
00:45:04,360 --> 00:45:05,320
Deng Ligang got away.

752
00:45:06,230 --> 00:45:07,070
Is this a farewell dinner?

753
00:45:13,440 --> 00:45:14,550
One popsicle, please.

754
00:45:14,920 --> 00:45:15,360
Okay.

755
00:45:18,800 --> 00:45:19,550
How much?

756
00:45:19,980 --> 00:45:20,740
Fifty cents.

757
00:45:27,670 --> 00:45:28,110
Here.

758
00:45:28,550 --> 00:45:29,190
Here's your change.

759
00:45:41,590 --> 00:45:42,230
Thank you.

760
00:45:44,530 --> 00:45:46,170
At that moment, I didn't know

761
00:45:46,710 --> 00:45:47,630
that in three days,

762
00:45:48,110 --> 00:45:50,070
this girl's parents would report her missing

763
00:45:50,780 --> 00:45:51,650
to the police.
